# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# Example: feat(portal): add progress tracking dashboard
#
# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
# Scope: marketing, portal, shared, config, docs
# Subject: imperative mood, max 50 chars

# Body: Explain *what* and *why* (not how), wrap at 72 chars
# Include motivation, previous behavior, and new behavior

# Footer: Reference issues, breaking changes
# Fixes #123
# BREAKING CHANGE: description

# Remember:
# - One commit = one logical change
# - Include tests with features
# - Update docs in same commit
# - Think about educational value